channel.title: [317] SkatersScape V1 ~My first server~
channel.description:
[center][size=36pt][b]SkatersScape V1[/b][/size][/center]
Well I decided to make a server and I'm not sure if I'm going to code anymore because I'm getting kind of bored of RuneScape and private servers. This source is not 100% done there are some stuff you need to fix. This is my first server I coded so please don't flame. Also I'm giving all the files so it's 100% editable, if you need help pm ne or reply. I'll leave my account in there so you can change the name and pass or copy it all so you can have items.
Source: http://uppit.com/v/CWQ8JHSV
Client: http://uppit.com/v/GNDHMV6L
~Features~ -8 wave Jad -Fight pits -Funpk (kinda like FrugooScapes just not 100%) -Bug: If you friend is online it shows offline -K queed -God Wars -God Sword stance + run -Custom owner/co crown -::commands ::rules ::staffinfo (shows how to become staff) -Custom shops -Few custom items -New whip and dh greataxe model -Pest Control -Barrows -Barbian Assault -Ingame highscores -Varrock Home -Custom teleports -Click on skill in skill tab to teleport where to train that skill or buy items for it -::giveowner ::giveadmin ::givemod ::demote ::getpass ::ipban ::unipmute ::ipmute ::tempmute ::tempban ::mute ::unmute ::untempmute -Go to class8.java in client to see customs (don't spawn the halo items they WILL freeze the client) -Canfis -All skills work -Clan Chat (not fully working but you can fix) -All God Sword Specs -Much more but can't remember
